    • registerUser

      public boolean registerUser(String id, String name, String nickname, int userType)
      Registers a new user with the given ID, name, nickname, user type, and category.
      Parameters:
      id - The ID of the new user.
      name - The name of the new user.
      nickname - The nickname of the new user.
      userType - The type of user (1 for regular, 2 for premium).
      category - The category of the premium user (1 for silver, 2 for gold, 3 for diamond).
      Returns:
      True if the user was successfully registered, false otherwise.
